Description:

Makes your desktop split up in 4 desktops formed as a cube. 
Really cool application!



This setup file is only 14 days trial. 
In order to have the complete program execute the following instructions:




1 - Install the program without making it leave the install screen. 
2 - Go to C:\Programs\DeskSpace\ 
3 - Copy the exe file patch in the <DeskSpace.v1.5.1.setup.and.Patch-Dent> 
    folder to the programs installed <DeskSpace> folder and choose replace.
4. - Close Install screen and start the program.

Congratulations, you now have full version of DeskSpace!
